    "In order to identify source and target domains for M-JDA, the LUMO mast is first viewed as a homogeneous population.",
    "To localize severe damage states by transferring knowledge from minor damage states, the LUMO structure is considered a homogeneous population with a source and target domains.",
    "The source domain includes the data collected during the minor damage states.",
    "The target domain includes data collected during the severe damage states.",
    "Table 3 presents the way in which the data has been separated."
